# Human backstop to the automated `guard` check (.github/workflows/guard.yml).
# These paths define what counts as a valid submission — verifiers, CI, shared
# tooling, mission specs — so only the maintainer may change them. When branch
# protection has "Require review from Code Owners" on, a PR touching any of
# these needs @timqian's review before it can merge.
#
# Deliberately NOT a catch-all (`*`): plain record submissions under
# missions/<id>/records/*.json must stay mergeable on green CI without a manual
# review gate.

/.github/                @timqian
/tools/                  @timqian
/skill.md                @timqian
/CONTRIBUTING.md         @timqian
/README.md               @timqian

# Per-mission spec + verifier (matches new missions and edits to existing ones).
**/verify.py             @timqian
**/meta.json             @timqian
**/mission.md            @timqian
**/challenge/            @timqian
